We can see in the simulated robot that each link has different colors and textures. The 
following tags inside the .xacro file provide textures and colors to robot links:
 <gazebo reference="bottom_link"> 
 <material>Gazebo/White</material> 
 </gazebo> 
 <gazebo reference="base_link"> 
 <material>Gazebo/White</material> 
 </gazebo> 
 <gazebo reference="shoulder_pan_link"> 
 <material>Gazebo/Red</material> 
 </gazebo>
